org.geppetto.model.values

Interface VisualGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISynchable, Node
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VisualGroupImpl

    public interface VisualGroup
extends Node
    A representation of the model object 'Visual Group'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Low Spectrum Color
    • High Spectrum Color
    • Type
    • Visual Group Elements
    See Also:
    ValuesPackage.getVisualGroup()
